      "term": "simplicially",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "null",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "adverb",
          "definition": "in a simple or straightforward manner, or in a way that relates to simplicity",
          "examples": [
            "The theorem is presented simplicially to help beginners understand the concept.",
            "He explained the process simplicially, using plain examples."
